description:
On December 10th, experience the musical of a lifestime... Sonic Underground: Highschool Musical
Starring: 
Bartleby Montlcair of Dresdin (And his boyfriend Sonic)
Knuckles the Echidna
Sonia the Hedgehog
Manic the hedgehog
And many many more.
If you like my work consider supporting me on patreon like a good boy or girl
https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
